snippet.title: Hotel Quartier Bassin, Maastricht YOU TUBE
snippet.description:
Hotel Quartier Bassin, Maastricht YOU TUBE
Toegevoegd door hotelsnlvideos 5 jaren geleden
Hotel Prins Hendrik is located on the corner of the 'Zeedijk', where an abundance of bars and restaurants can be found. Hotel Quartier Bassin is established in a historical building dating back to the year 1700 and is located within a brief stroll from the centre of the cosy city of Maastricht. The building consists of a front house and a back house, divided by a patio area. The original name of the building was 'In den Raeven' and this can still be read on one of the original stones on the façade of the hotel. Visit us : http://www.hotels.nl/maastricht/quartier/

snippet.title: Hotel Botticelli Maastricht
snippet.description:
Hotel Botticelli Maastricht
Toegevoegd door hotelsnl 3 jaren geleden
Hotel Botticelli is an extraordinary 3-star hotel in the heart of Maastricht. The special interiors of the hotel are inspired by Italian Renaissance art, and are furnished with artistic and stylish decorations and furniture. The hotel, which is situated on the famous city square Vrijthof, is also close to the most important historic attractions, restaurants, and bars that Maastricht has to offer. Click here for more information:http://www.hotels.nl/maastricht/botticelli/
